Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:06.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.72,0:00:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世上奇妙之事實在太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.82,0:00:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從天上掉下來了好多好多的糖果和點心
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.40,0:00:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.49,0:00:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.72,0:00:23.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是神北同學吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝…君？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.45,0:00:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是生活指導的老師在模仿直枝君的聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.25,0:00:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有老師會懂這種特技
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.89,0:00:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.16,0:00:43.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.21,0:00:44.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在就…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.79,0:00:50.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦呀  出不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.36,0:00:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝君拉我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.59,0:00:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:56.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.23,0:01:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.09,0:01:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食蟻獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許是犰狳？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.86,0:01:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.67,0:01:16.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  神北同學
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.84,0:01:22.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是你的裙子被什麼東西給鉤住了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.28,0:01:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.24,0:01:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  直枝君
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,食蟻獸？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.51,0:01:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  原來真是食蟻獸啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.84,0:01:44.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被  被看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.68,0:01:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦  沒人肯嫁給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.21,0:01:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本來就不會有人嫁給你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.49,0:01:57.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只好努力嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.18,0:01:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  請加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:01.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.89,0:02:06.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當是沒看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.14,0:02:08.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:10.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當是沒被看到吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣問題就都解決了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.80,0:02:18.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就…這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.95,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然難得來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.58,0:02:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You來嚐嚐這個甜甜圈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.87,0:02:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茶也有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我最喜歡的地方  經常會上來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  被太多人知道的話會有各種各樣的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.90,0:02:48.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以要對別人保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.70,0:02:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.77,0:02:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣一來你也是共犯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.68,0:02:57.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:02.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學真的很喜歡吃甜食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.88,0:03:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是我的Happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃點心的時候會感覺很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:13.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然微不足道  但能因此覺得幸福就很了不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.44,0:03:16.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以說甜食很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.04,0:03:19.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:25.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直枝君變得幸福的話我會很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.81,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別人幸福的話  自己也會有點點幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.73,0:03:35.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幸福的話  我也幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.33,0:03:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我幸福的話  你也幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直一直循環下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.97,0:03:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  幸福螺旋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.37,0:03:51.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實  打心底去相信這個理論的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:54.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許真能稍稍使人變得幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.74,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高興直枝君能過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是同班同學卻沒有說過話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了  我是來邀請你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.15,0:04:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請我？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:12.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組建了一支草根棒球隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.27,0:04:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過因為隊員不夠所以還在找人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.94,0:04:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒球？  草？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四號三壘手是蒲公英嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小草打棒球…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.70,0:04:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得打不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.86,0:04:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  不是說小草打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.67,0:04:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是指在藍天下悠閒地打棒球的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.52,0:04:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悠閒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.06,0:04:39.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學不管怎麼看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.54,0:04:45.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都似乎跟棒球無緣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.47,0:06:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快餓死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開飯咯開飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:24.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.64,0:06:25.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}小氣鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}你說誰是小氣鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.22,0:06:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}好啦好啦  這份給你  就別鬧了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.12,0:06:31.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}本來就是你的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.59,0:06:32.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}哪裡錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.58,0:06:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}搶了我的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.95,0:06:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}肌肉需要碳水化合物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}你說什麼  快還我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}有啥關係  為了我的肌肉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.77,0:06:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們組建了棒球隊  Little Busters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.49,0:06:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了謙吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隊員有真人  鈴  我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.56,0:06:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.94,0:06:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喲  大清早的在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.99,0:06:44.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為這笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:47.22,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}別叫我笨蛋  好好叫我肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.31,0:06:48.17,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}誰會叫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.51,0:06:45.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有恭介
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.61,0:06:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,僅此四人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.48,0:06:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來組樂隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.03,0:06:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂隊名叫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.57,0:06:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Little Busters！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.84,0:06:58.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樂隊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭介等等  不是棒球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊對  是棒球來著
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:06.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到樂隊漫畫被感動就情不自禁了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.74,0:07:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本就無所謂的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.25,0:07:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來組建棒球隊也只是一時興起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:15.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  還少五個隊員吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.14,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趕快湊齊來打棒球揮灑青春的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.22,0:07:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想做的才不是棒球這種拐彎抹角的運動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.65,0:07:27.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是直接以拳腳相交的熱血戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.03,0:07:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.87,0:07:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我一邊去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.26,0:07:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:33.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴  躲開
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.10,0:07:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,劍豪塚原卜傳？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.82,0:07:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.14,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就這麼放開它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.65,0:08:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你  你找打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.44,0:08:05.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人惡人先告狀了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.70,0:08:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我求之不得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這邊也當真了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器  給我武器
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.78,0:08:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.11,0:08:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的是肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.09,0:08:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肥皂？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Battle Start！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.86,0:08:26.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我泡沫男！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.53,0:08:32.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他這是想幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:33.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼是肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,井之原真人  我授予你光榮稱號
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.67,0:08:42.63,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(320,332,320,325,0,700)\fad(700,0)}真人獲得了稱號「忘記把腦子放哪兒了的男人」！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.07,0:08:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還少五名隊員嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.25,0:08:55.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都高二了  這個時候還會有人願意來打棒球嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.79,0:08:57.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更何況  要的是整整五個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.82,0:09:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吶  知道棗鈴去哪裡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.61,0:09:03.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明到她值日  卻沒有擦黑板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在和貓一起玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她滿腦子全是貓的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.77,0:09:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了自己和貓  其他什麼東西都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  仗著自己在男生裡有那麼點人氣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.51,0:09:18.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊  來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  五十六
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:26.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅持住  堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.86,0:09:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這可是史無前例的雙足步行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是在這裡嗎  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.79,0:09:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.57,0:09:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然是值日生就不能四處瞎玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.32,0:09:42.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好好完成自己該做的工作的話  會被大家排擠的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:45.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和班上女生們的關係也不怎麼樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.91,0:09:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.19,0:09:49.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那有和你關係不錯的女生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.55,0:09:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在我後面的女生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.50,0:09:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,名字叫什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.53,0:09:55.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這也能叫關係不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.81,0:09:58.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了  閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有朋友不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.48,0:10:02.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.02,0:10:03.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是說你會死嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.53,0:10:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還有一起長大的我們在你身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.54,0:10:11.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但以後畢業了什麼的  那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多管閒事大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.00,0:10:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,列儂這樣說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:18.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.02,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.05,0:10:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.09,0:10:24.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像寫著什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.43,0:10:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.53,0:10:32.70,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\1c&000000&\fs20}這個世界裡存在著秘密\N如果想知道的話\N就去完成全部的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.76,0:10:32.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個世界裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.99,0:10:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…存在著秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.18,0:10:50.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密  指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.35,0:10:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  還有哦
Comment: 0,0:10:56.85,0:11:01.35,up,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\bord0\1c&000000&\b1}給你們布置第一個課題\N去解決男生宿舍雜物間的衛生問題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.03,0:10:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給你們布置第一個課題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.27,0:11:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去解決男生宿舍雜物間的衛生問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.22,0:11:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰寫的這封信
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.23,0:11:07.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是貓寫的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.71,0:11:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貓不可能會寫信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.18,0:11:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,悄悄跟在列儂後面的話  說不定就能知道犯人是誰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:16.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  那樣總覺得有點卑鄙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:18.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想挑戰這個課題？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.72,0:11:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完成它不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是個孩子氣的惡作劇罷了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是別人想出來捉弄人的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.86,0:11:27.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想去確認一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認犯人？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:31.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確認那人想要告訴我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴的眼中充滿了躍躍欲試的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像貓兒看見毛茸茸的怪東西在眼前晃來晃去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.11,0:11:42.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不禁想要去追逐一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  在這個世界裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.40,0:11:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底有著什麼樣的秘密呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:54.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的只是這一成不變的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平靜的日常生活而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.92,0:11:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說有什麼讓我略微不安的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.84,0:12:06.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Narcolepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.80,0:12:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我從小時候起就落下的疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗜睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.80,0:12:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知自己何時會失去意識陷入沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.35,0:12:27.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想讓你來擔任四號擊球手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.92,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來做四號？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.49,0:12:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去最弱小的理樹
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.82,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸成長為最強的四號擊球手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才是觀眾最想看到的劇情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪來的觀眾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.07,0:12:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明只有四名隊員
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本談不上什麼四號擊球手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:48.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看看啊  這身肌肉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.47,0:12:49.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣  怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們幾個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:52.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別磨磨蹭蹭的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.84,0:12:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去解決男生宿舍雜物間的衛生問題了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.64,0:13:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這裡嗎  雜物間
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.69,0:13:08.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確有夠嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.06,0:13:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上一次掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是明治維新前夜了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.67,0:13:15.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的要打掃啊  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.04,0:13:16.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.36,0:13:20.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個嘛  雖然能整理乾淨是最好的了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.21,0:13:24.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  為什麼連我都必須來參加掃除啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:27.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老實說我只要一開始掃除
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.73,0:13:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚臍就會因特異體質而瘙癢難耐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.37,0:13:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不禁跳起「肌肉YEAHYEAH」的舞來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還真是找到寶貝了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個系列一本不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.77,0:13:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡也有
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.80,0:13:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  別把馬上就要整理的東西翻得到處都是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.69,0:13:49.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.14,0:13:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我啊  決定了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:14:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受你們的邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.38,0:14:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小草打棒球
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能幫上直枝君的忙我非常非常開心
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.59,0:14:10.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.45,0:14:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍  稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.11,0:14:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說你打算加入Little Busters嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.42,0:14:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棗同學也是隊員之一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.18,0:14:27.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好高興
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.55,0:14:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.04,0:14:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起努力打棒球吧  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.35,0:14:34.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:36.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴極端怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.27,0:14:38.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接得好  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:48.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.25,0:14:56.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒  沒事吧  神北同學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  鈴  快道歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.87,0:15:04.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的  沒事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.43,0:15:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  你是叫神北吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.24,0:15:19.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼戴著獨指手套
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.59,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為  打棒球的時候要用到的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.41,0:15:26.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點東西我還是知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.87,0:15:30.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉  打棒球時要用的並不是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.50,0:15:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該戴的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這種
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也不是那個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:38.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}被忽略掉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.12,0:15:40.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過在成為隊員之前  有件事很在意
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.26,0:15:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在意的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.32,0:15:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來就是打掃衛生了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.30,0:15:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然這樣就沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就當是順便鍛鍊肌肉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.78,0:15:56.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,課題  要完成的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肌肉YEAHYEAH
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  居然能打掃得這麼乾淨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都想表揚我自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是你的功勞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鈴不去道謝是不行的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.94,0:16:33.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多虧了神北同學  才完成了課題呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.81,0:16:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  這樣一來棒球部的活動室也打掃得乾乾淨淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's打棒球了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.97,0:16:46.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.58,0:16:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡不是棒球部的活動室哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.15,0:16:52.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.30,0:17:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三四…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.76,0:17:03.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙沒問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.81,0:17:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不妙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:07.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要說有多不妙的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.30,0:17:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眉頭已經皺到回不來的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她本人倒是幹勁十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.91,0:17:15.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來她充滿了不安因素
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先來做個入團測試吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.78,0:17:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,順理成章地在她不合格後委婉拒絕嗎  挺方便啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.95,0:17:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.17,0:17:30.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,測試？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:31.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  第一問
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.60,0:17:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為打棒球所必需的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.13,0:17:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.94,0:17:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.29,0:17:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…友情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.74,0:17:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.39,0:17:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.91,0:17:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我等等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我會加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.86,0:17:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是失態了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.82,0:17:54.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不小心被這太過於標準的答案給感動到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.68,0:17:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,測試一般都是測運動能力之類的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:18:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,體…體力之類的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別把肌肉給忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.20,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.01,0:18:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼首先進行擊球測試
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.60,0:18:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是看不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.35,0:18:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來  把球棒給我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,塑膠球棒要輕很多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.81,0:18:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.50,0:18:28.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.83,0:18:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不  問題多到數不清
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.12,0:18:36.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來是跑壘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.23,0:18:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後是守壘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.78,0:18:41.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是真正的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.50,0:18:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22\an8}蒲公英先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這沒戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.16,0:18:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.05,0:18:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  最後的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.80,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再問你一次
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.49,0:19:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為打棒球所必需的是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.15,0:19:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.15,0:19:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:08.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毅力
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.53,0:19:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.55,0:19:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以及…友情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然還是合格
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.13,0:19:15.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北小毬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.17,0:19:18.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身上已經具備了打棒球所必需的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.34,0:19:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,入團決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從今天起  你就是我們Little Busters的一員了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.55,0:19:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底算哪門子的測試…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今後請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.28,0:19:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的話叫我小毬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:40.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還在怕生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.80,0:19:41.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.89,0:19:42.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別躲了  鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:45.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請多指教哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.08,0:19:46.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.40,0:19:50.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴什麼的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.43,0:19:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很困擾！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.91,0:19:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.94,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她只是還不太習慣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:20:00.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道該如何回應你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.97,0:20:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為她從沒被人叫做過小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.03,0:20:07.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼我就是小肌肉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後要叫我小肌肉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.14,0:20:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噁心死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.15,0:20:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘁…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.92,0:20:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還覺得挺好聽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.37,0:20:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒…沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.57,0:20:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.03,0:20:23.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真人從以前開始就一直這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.94,0:20:28.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:34.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小鈴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.93,0:20:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.29,0:20:40.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神北同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.29,0:20:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.93,0:20:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.43,0:20:59.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.33,0:21:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幫我縫裙子…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:21:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我抓
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.32,0:21:06.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搔癢癢癢癢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不禁再次祈求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣快樂的時光能永遠持續下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世界的秘密  指的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.19,0:21:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像往常一樣  突然降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗜睡症
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.62,0:21:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs18\pos(320,328)}Narcolepsy
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.79,0:21:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我與這個世界的接點被斷開
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.48,0:21:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陷入了沉睡之中
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//--------------------NEXT--------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.33,0:23:28.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被邀請去參加迷一樣的茶會了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰誘惑理樹的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.27,0:23:32.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出類拔萃的智商
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.60,0:23:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,神乎其神的運動神經
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.24,0:23:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是無敵的那個人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.96,0:23:36.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邀請她加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.33,0:23:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mission  Start！
